{"tid":1186262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問6月9號上街有咩用？","createTime":"2019-06-04T21:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T02:01:14.000Z","uid":21394,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e95a890084c34608f669f888b9fecdc69f1467f","tid":1186262,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T21:52:37.000Z","msg":"上次雨革都失敗啦，社運低潮左咁耐⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我自己上街既目的就係話比中共聽，<br />\n只要個特首唔係無篩選香港一人一票選出來，<br />\n真正代表香港人，<br />\n冇人可以做得長。<br />\n我地一定會令佢變成跛腳鴨，<br />\n話比政府知賣港係要付出代價，<br />\n<br />\n上一次人人個都期望好大，<br />\n一個Bad end令好多人失望，<br />\n邊有社會運動可以一次就成功㗎？<br />\n2014年讓我見到香港人嗰種美麗既人格，<br />\n一種只係存在係從前父母口耳相傳既人鄰關係，<br />\n堅強、友善、自律、忍耐。<br />\n我見到香港人有既呢D特質，<br />\n漸漸比無聊既猜疑同陰謀論遮蓋。<br />\n<br />\n我成日覺得，<br />\n只要每個人做好自己既本份，<br />\n哩個社會已經可以不一樣。<br />\n6月9號，香港再一次需要香港人去守護，<br />\n我會去盡我既責任同力量，<br />\n香港人，你願意守護香港嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GuSNjkr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGuSNjkr.png&h=92d18958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6412d469d54255eac797c5a9ebf7cf5acdd81a3","tid":1186262,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T21:59:06.000Z","msg":"負皮都留言講下點解負皮吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f19e91dc8a579bc2c15aee446d3eb640027517","tid":1186262,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:00:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cf85d1f6244143417c37294aa04ce073133921","tid":1186262,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:04:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698f43eac0281fc4e3c92a3ffae73329f5b5a950","tid":1186262,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T22:11:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f7ae39bc16db7cdde5e5e017a60b3cdbb1f1bd"